#  Firebase security is enforced by Firestore Rules, NOT by hiding them.
#  STILL: paste your **ROTATED** keys here (the ones shared in chat are burned).
#
#  Copy this file to `.env.local` (already gitignored) and fill in.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
